islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T08:13:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"078a9724d2527cffab26f44ffa9daa4c9b373809","tid":314013,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實我唔係好明神駒做乜柒，初時追住泛民黎屌，吹奏熱狗，而家連熱狗都屌埋，佢係咪想自己出黎組黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫過熱狗就唔屌得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我信過泛民大台又轉左去本土係咪唔可以屌泛民?<br />\nBTW 神驅早兩三年都有出書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n關屌唔屌柒熱狗撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇話唔屌得，而家全世界佢都屌，咪問係咪想自己選囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌曬全世界同出唔出黎選有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n上去高登同連登，都大把人屌哂全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359b46bf253b2a5bfe76ac27242cf244238b1669","tid":314013,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T08:45:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}